---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Chainlink SmartCon 2023 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Barcelona, Spain</div>
        <div class="event-title">Chainlink<br />SmartCon<br />2023</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          A 4-day event for 1,500 attendees and 30 sponsors — 4 stages of content over 2 days, preceded by a 2-day Hacker House targeting developers.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Format</div>
            <p>The SmartCon format pairs a developer-focused Hacker House with the main conference to serve two distinct but connected audiences. Barcelona gave us the infrastructure to execute both at scale — a modern convention space for the conference days and intimate venues for the developer programming.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>Four simultaneous stages required a production team that could run independently while staying coordinated. The main stage was a full theatrical build — LED wall, custom scenic, and a lighting package that made every panel and keynote feel like a headline moment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Evening Events</div>
            <p>Barcelona's architecture gave us incredible options for the closing events. We took over a historic venue in the heart of the city — vaulted ceilings, dramatic lighting, and a production design that fully transformed the space into a SmartCon experience unlike anything a hotel ballroom could offer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
